==English==

===Expression===
'''[[you're|you’re]] [[welcome]]!'''

# (after receiving [[thanks]]) Don’t worry

====Synonyms====
*[[don't mention it|don’t mention it]]
*[[no worries]] {{italbrac|Australia|informal}}

